   129. La Canada Flintridge, CA....(18,560).......($ 500,000) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   130. Lincoln, MA.................(7,757)........($ 500,000) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   131. Villanova, PA...............(7,573)........($ 500,000) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   132. Long Grove, IL..............(6,018)........($ 497,000) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   133. Barrington Hills, IL........(4,799)........($ 495,500) &QL;
</P>
<P>
