<P>
   REDWHITE-BURGERS _ Fun trivia for Fourth of July food on that
food trio _ burger, ketchup, mayo. Trivia box on each, including
myths and food safety tips. (Salsa does not outsell ketchup in
numbers of bottles. it does outsell in dollar amounts. Mayo does
not make your food spoil more; in fact, it helps retard bacterial
growth. Cooking a burger it until it is brown is no guarantee that
it is safe.) (Crider, Austin American-Statesman).
