   ONBUSINESS-COLUMN (Undated) _ Most people have never heard of
Tyco International. But Tyco, operating out of a small building in
Exeter, N.H., commands a market value in excess of Gillette and
Raytheon together. By Steven Syre and Charles Stein. PHOTO
