<P>
   A Space Odyssey,'' ``A Clockwork Orange,'' ``Barry Lyndon,''
``The Shining,'' ``Full Metal Jacket,'' VHS, $19.98, DVD, $24.98.
Federico Fellini, restored director's cut: ``Nights of Cabiria,''
VHS $29.95, DVD $39.95. Peter Weir: ``The Truman Show,''
``Gallipoli,'' ``Witness,'' VHS, $14.95, DVD, $29.99.
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  TV: ``A Tad More Jeeves &AMP; Wooster,'' six volumes, $79.95.
Masterpiece Theatre: ``Great Expectations,'' two tapes, $29.98.
