   UNDATED _ Kids shouldn't have all the fun this weekend. Jolly up
the festivities for the grown-ups with some upscale takes on
childhood summer favorites. Add a splash of tequila to the
Popsicles, some white wine to the lemonade, and have yourself a
sparkling Fourth. And don't forget to run through the sprinklers.
By BEVERLY BUNDY. Story will move in ``d'' food and dining
category. &QL; 
