<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-GORTON-SPI </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
GORTON MAKING SURE HE'S NOT VULNERABLE ON HEALTH ISSUE AT
RE-ELECTION TIME 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 By MICHAEL PAULSON  
 c.1999 Seattle Post-Intelligencer  
